 -- Function: ax_bar (CATEGORIES, VALUES)
     Bar chart for labeled or numeric data.  Use inside ‘ax_draw2d’.

     Calling forms:

        • ‘ax_bar(categories, values)’ -- string category list + numeric
          value list
        • ‘ax_bar(values)’ -- just values (auto-numbered 1, 2, 3, ...)

     For multiple series, use different ‘name’ options and ‘bar_mode’
     layout option.

